 <h2 class="mb-4 font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal sm:text-4xl">Embroidery</h2>
 <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ash">
 Commercial embroidery on polos, softshells, caps, beanies, jackets, and bags. The decoration that reads "professional" the second somebody walks into a client meeting or picks up a permit. Sharp, durable, and a clear notch above heat-applied vinyl on gear your name tag is going to live on.
 </p>
 <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-ash">
 Up to 15 thread colors per design. Standard placements: left chest, right sleeve, back yoke, cap front, and cap back. Free logo digitizing on your first order. Tight trade tolerances — we match your logo within 1–2 Pantone shades using Madeira Classic threads.
 </p>
