 </div>
 <div class="border border-hairline bg-panel p-3">
 <div class="spec text-gold-600">Digitizing</div>
 <div class="mt-1 font-heading text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal">Free 1st order</div>
 </div>
